{"tid":2055084,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"司機吐露港釀連環車禍　險掃低3名交通警","createTime":"2020-06-07T16:18:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-27T05:12:16.000Z","uid":240362,"like":122,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"232ed7da82dbddff7d8ca0205c9916681f7002c0","tid":2055084,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T16:18:22.000Z","msg":"吐露港公路發生驚險車禍，昨晚(7日)7時許，一輛農夫車沿大埔吐露港公路往粉嶺方向行駛，至近康樂園附近懷疑失控，撞向路旁石壆後反彈回中線，涉事農夫車車頭損毀嚴重，男司機手部受傷及胸口痛楚，及後由救護車送往大埔那打素醫院治理。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，當數名警員在場調查意外期間，一輛客貨車尾隨而至，疑該車司機未有為意前方發生車禍，並沿第3線爬頭；詎料客貨車司機切回行車線時，始驚覺前方車禍現場有3名交通警員已落地調查意外，客貨車司機隨即連忙扭軚閃避，惟失控撞壆，繼而衝前約數十米停下。事件中，客貨車男司機未有受傷，惟上址一帶交通因而受阻。<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=jILigwfPQQ17AL812Qo3KdB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=ddf92fa0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>"},{"pid":"4681c4ede4c0ac7bdf3cc8f5de194f4d365c9c98","tid":2055084,"uid":359022,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T16:18:44.000Z","msg":"rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f48cc510029dee4e42d4668c35b58c79963fafab","tid":2055084,"uid":240362,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"quote":{"pid":"4681c4ede4c0ac7bdf3cc8f5de194f4d365c9c98","tid":2055084,"uid":359022,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T16:18:44.000Z","msg":"rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T16:19:11.000Z","msg":"險掃低."},{"pid":"53c686900ff24dbbaf27c4e376c4be8bb0fa43ad","tid":2055084,"uid":359022,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"quote":{"pid":"f48cc510029dee4e42d4668c35b58c79963fafab","tid":2055084,"uid":240362,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"quote":{"pid":"4681c4ede4c0ac7bdf3cc8f5de194f4d365c9c98","tid":2055084,"uid":359022,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T16:18:44.000Z","msg":"rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3